HOUSE BILL NO. HB0155
Workplace violence in health care.
Sponsored by: Representative(s) Brown, L, Angelos,
Clouston, Filer, Geringer and Harshman and
Senator(s) Barlow, Brennan and Crago
A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to workplace safety; requiring the
2 department of workforce services to compile reports of
3 workplace violence in hospitals, health care clinics and
4 long term care facilities as specified; requiring
5 reporting; providing definitions; requiring rulemaking; and
6 providing for effective dates.
7
8 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
9
10 Section 1.
11
12 (a) Every hospital, health care clinic and long-term
13 care facility that receives any state funds shall be
14 required to report to the department of workforce services
